Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Government unable to vouch for nuclear safety
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bxnp
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 Apr 1979
Government admits being unable to guarantee nuclear reactor safety. Public support for nuclear power industry slumps. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less